---
title: Roasted Brussels Sprout and Barley Salad with Goat Cheese, Cranberries and Pepitas
description: Brussels sprouts are the “it” vegetable of the season—and for good reason! They become nutty and caramelized after a quick roast in the oven. Tossed over a barley salad with crunchy pepitas, sweet cranberries, and tangy goat cheese, this is one salad that is guaranteed to satisfy all your cravings.
